summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Taylor Avenue from the south line of Prospect Street to the north line of Lynn street et al in the City of Seattle, by paving same with asphalt under Ordinance No. 19651, creating Local Improvement District No. 1901 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
